<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="sports">Sports</h3>
<ol>
<li><p>How do I place a bet?</p>
<p>At SportyBet, you are free to place all kinds of bets: Singles, Multiples and System (combined) bets.</p>
<p>Multiple and System bets may include different sports: football, tennis, basketball, etc.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is the minimum and maximum stake for a bet and for a ticket?</p>
<p>The minimum stake amount for a ticket is NGN 100, and the maximum stake amount is NGN 2,000,000.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is the maximum payout?</p>
<p>The maximum payout for a bet is NGN 4,000,000.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where can I see my Sport bets?</p>
<p>Login into your account, click on &quot;Me&quot; in the bottom of Home page,  go to &quot;SPORTS BET HISTORY&quot; highlighted in green, then you can see both settled and unsettled bets.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where can I see my Virtual bets?</p>
<p>Go to Virtuals and click on &quot;<img src="../../../../assets/app-virtual.png" alt="">&quot; on the top-right corner of the page. You will find a list of all bets you have placed.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Can I cancel a bet?</p>
<p>No. A confirmed bet cannot be cancelled for any reason.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is a “Void Bet”?</p>
<p>&quot;Void Bet&quot; means the bet is either nil or invalid. This occurs when an event is postponed, or an event&#39;s results are unverifiable, among other circumstances. Once a match has been set as void (which will considered has having an odd of 1.00), other selections of a winning ticket will then be paid out regularly. If you are unsure about why your bet has been marked as &quot;Void&quot;, please contact us.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where can I find statistics for real sports?</p>
<p>For your assistance, SportyBet Nigeria provides statistical information on events as reference during betting.</p>
<p>Just click on &quot;<img src="../../../../assets/stats.jpg" alt="">&quot; in every single event detail page to take an advantage of this service.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where I can find the results of an event that has ended?</p>
<p>For your assistance, SportyBet Nigeria provides information about the results of events. Simply click on “Results” at the Homepage to easily check all the results of the events in which you are interested.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is Live Betting?</p>
<p>Live Betting is an exciting form of wagering that allows you to place bets on ongoing events. The odds are dynamic and change in accordance to the course of the actual event, offering double the excitement as you get to monitor the event while it is being played.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is banker?</p>
<p>A banker is a selection which a customer believes is certain to win. If a banker is selected, it will be included in every combination. Only winning bets provide return to the customer.</p>
</li>
</ol>
